      <installation_data><![CDATA[For the installation the major issue to take in to account is the correct installation of the bituminous layer to avoid infiltrations of water into the building. Also the colocation of the insulation layer should be verified in order to avoid possible thermal bridges. For the installation of the bitumen felt layer it is needed a professional that will use a fire pipe to fix the bitumen layer to the concrete slope]]></installation_data>
      <maintenance_data><![CDATA[Revisions should be done in order to check no infiltrations or degradations in the bituminous layer]]></maintenance_data>
